\v 28 \wj \+w Porque|strong="G1063"\+w* Âż\+w quiĂŠn|strong="G5101"\+w* \+w de|strong="G1537"\+w* ustedes \+w que|strong="G3588"\+w* \+w quiere|strong="G2309"\+w* \+w edificar|strong="G3618"\+w* \+w una|strong="G3588"\+w* \+w torre|strong="G4444"\+w*, \+w no|strong="G3780"\+w* se sienta \+w primero|strong="G4413"\+w* \+w y|strong="G1063"\+w* calcula \+w el|strong="G3588"\+w* costo, \+w si|strong="G1487"\+w* \+w tiene|strong="G2192"\+w* \+w para|strong="G1519"\+w* terminarla?\wj*  
